description:
After winning her first match she fell to the veteran Jester; however, the Deceptacon is strong and learns fast. With two matches under her belt, she is looking for another win and to move up in the rankings.

The Grappler showed serious skills against the Scorpion, but it is hard to gauge her true ability since the Scorpion holds the record for losing at US. Add to that the Grappler’s other win against Kat, and we still do not have a standard to judge the Grappler by. The one thing I do know with certainty is that the Grappler has a mad strap on technique, and really knows how to dish out a rd4 fucking.
title: The Deceptacon (1-1) The Grappler (2-2)
